'''Ludwig van Beethoven''' ({{Pron-en|ˈlʊdvɪɡ væn ˈbeɪtoʊvən}} (US) atau {{IPA-en|ˈbeɪt.hoʊvən|}} (UK); {{IPA-de|ˈluːtvɪç fan ˈbeːt.hoːfn̩|lang|De-Ludwig_van_Beethoven.ogg}}; dibaptis 17 Desember 1770<ref>Beethoven was [[baptism|baptised]] on 17 December. His date of birth was often, in the past, given as 16 December, however this is not known with certainty; his family celebrated his birthday on that date, but there is no documentary evidence that his birth was actually on 16 December.</ref> – wafat 26 Maret 1827) saurang pengarang dan pamain piano dari [[Jerman]]. Inyo dianggap menjadi tokoh penting pado maso peralihan musik klasik jo musik roman di era perkembangan musik di Barat, dan tetap menjadi salah saurang pengarang nan berpengaruh sepanjang maso.

